Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20140108  3 A History Hour: Jefferson and Hamilton


Prager H3: Dennis talks to John Ferling,

Prager H2: A wife is capable of emasculating her husband.

               And does she even know that she is doing it?

Prager H1: The LA County Board of Supervisors voted the cross
                                          back on the county seal.
             This is a battle Dennis has waged for 10 years.

          Sometimes it takes a while for the right thing to happen
